                             $TAB SYSTEM VARIABLE

  Edit 64 introduced the $tab system variable:

$Tab            STRING - A string containing a Tab character.

                           $STRFIX SYSTEM PROCEDURE

  Edit 65 introduced the $strfix system procedure:

$Strfix (address)
                STRING - Returns a string copied from the Asciz string found at
                Address. This  is  necessary  for  JSYSs'  that  produce  Asciz
                strings:  

        integer number,dummy;
        string username;
        ...
                                        ! allocate memory to store user nam
        dummy = $get_mem(50);
                                        ! do DIRST, storing name at dummy
        if $jsys(8%41 !{DIRST

                !  , byt_ptr_a(dummy), number) eql 0 then abort "dirst failure"
                + $lasterror; ! make a PCL string  username  =  $strfix(dummy);
                call $ret_mem(dummy,50); ! Memory is no longer needed.  display
                $username; }

